WEBVTT

00:00.125 --> 00:03.625
Gerda has two siblings 
 who do not go to school yet.

00:04.125 --> 00:09.625
Gerda's father died a few years ago 
 in a machine accident in the same factory

00:09.875 --> 00:12.125
where her mother still works today.

00:12.625 --> 00:14.375
Her mother works in shifts

00:14.625 --> 00:20.125
and often rents out her bed to so-called bed lodgers
 to have some extra income.

00:20.375 --> 00:23.375
Gerda is sometimes afraid of the strange men

00:23.500 --> 00:25.450
who spend the night in her small flat.

00:25.550 --> 00:29.875
But they need the extra money 
 for the ever-increasing rent.
